name: Mission #1 The Moon
description: Hi everyone! Welcome to the crew, my name is Quinn but you probably know me as the red Astrobro! Let’s run through this last mission huh?   Quinns log: We landed on the moon just a day ago, it’s cool but I see it whenever I look up. I wonder what the first new world will look like? We got out of there pretty fast. Once we were told to go to the shuttle we ran as fast as we could! Man, I'm excited for this adventure. “End Transmission”  P.S. Listen with sound done by the amazing @soyface
